download this file to this folder:
https://github.com/C1710/blobmoji/releases/download/v15.1-beta1/Blobmoji.ttf
and run `python subset_blobmoji.py` to generate the compressed blobmoji.woff2

DISCLAIMER: the reason the tool looks like an LLM obviously wrote it is because it was written by Claude Opus 4.6 :^)
